name: custom
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool seeding_data.
Tool description: Completely APIs that helps web developers and web designers generate fake data in a fast and easy way.
API description: Fetches custom data from the seeding-data API based on provided parameters.

vatid.description: The VAT ID to include in the query.

quantity.description: The number of rows to fetch.

birthday.description: The birthday to include in the query.

name.description: The first name to include in the query.

surname.description: The last name to include in the query.
